  <trk>
    <name>MXP-L3 — Liguria Coast Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from MXP and ride into the Liguria Coast. Hit Pavia and Portofino Viewpoint — 100m. Loop back to MXP over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
